  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study has the purpose to investigate the benefit of treating breast cancer patients in
      prone position. This treatment is compared to the standard technique in our center (supine
      position with or without respiratory gating). The investigators want to compare the doses on
      the organs at risk (heart and lungs) in the different techniques.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
